snippet.title: Fear Odyssey - Launch Trailer | Steam
snippet.description:
When fear is incarnated in our humanity, many things happen, good and bad, take control of this fear by mixing 2D and 3D dimensions and live a journey beyond Greece.

https://store.steampowered.com/app/2835430/Fear_Odyssey/

Fear Odyssey,  available NOW!
